12. Patja A, Makinen-Kiljunen S, Davidkin I,
Paunio M, Peltola H. Allergic reactions to
measles-mumps-rubella vaccination. Pediatrics. 2001 Feb;107(2):E27.

13. Patja A, Davidkin I, Kurki T, Kallio MJ,
